task.summary: Toodles is an app fr buying Bunny chows. It is an Android application that uses Google Cloud Enpoints as a backend and MySql database.
Changed the database string to the uat version on google cloud instance. Added Cron jobs to deal with the timeout of executing the endpoints.

Fixed User.js file and register.html file. Report is now pointing to cloud deployed endpoints.
Fixed the History activity issue as well

Added buttons to add and remove items from cart. Also added a text view to show how many of each individual items are added to the cart.
Creating a backgroud file for the add and remove button.

Added 4 Pojo files 2 in the mobile app and 2 in the back end. Added 1 DAO file Added a KasiLisAdapter class The files are Shop and Kasi
